      • T265Controller

        public T265Controller​(com.qualcomm.robotcore.hardware.HardwareMap hwMap,
                      org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.external.Telemetry telemetry)
        This is the main constructor of this class. It requires hardwareMap and telemetry objects, and it instantiates the camera object if it has not already been instantiated.
        Parameters:
        hwMap - the HardwareMap of the robot. Must be provided through the OpMode instantiating the controller.
        telemetry - the Telemetry object; used to send messages to the Driver Station.
